criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Subject was pregnant with a multiple gestation and received NIPT with the MaterniT21
             PLUS LDT and a valid test result is available;

          -  Subject was 18 years of age or older at the time of NIPT;

          -  Subject provides signed and dated informed consent in English;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Subjects' treating physician is not located in the United States.
